ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMERS:

1. UNOFFICIAL GARMIN API USAGE
This software uses the unofficial 'garminconnect' Python library which
reverse-engineers Garmin's web API. This may violate Garmin's Terms of Service.
Use at your own risk. The authors are not responsible for any consequences of
using unofficial APIs.

2. NOT MEDICAL ADVICE
This software provides training recommendations based on algorithms and AI
analysis. It is NOT medical advice and should not be used as a substitute for
professional medical consultation. Always consult healthcare professionals
before starting any training program or if you have health concerns.

3. AI ANALYSIS LIMITATIONS
AI-generated recommendations are based on available data and algorithms.
Individual responses to training vary. Users should use their own judgment
and listen to their bodies. The authors are not responsible for injuries,
overtraining, or other adverse outcomes.

4. DATA PRIVACY
Users are responsible for securing their own health data and API credentials.
The software stores data locally, but users should take appropriate security
measures including encryption and backups.

5. COST DISCLAIMER
This software requires paid API services (Claude AI) which incur costs.
Users are responsible for all API costs incurred through usage.

